title: House Dems rally against ICE funding just one year after dozens broke ranks on immigration
description: Only seven Democrats voted to give ICE more money on Thursday, a stark contrast from the 42 who backed the Laken Riley Act.
content: Only seven Democrats voted to give ICE more money on Thursday, a stark contrast from the 42 who backed the Laken Riley Act.
